<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://gohugo.io/" version="0.82.0">Hugo</generator><title type="html">grim on Sebastian Hoß</title><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/grim/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="HTML"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/grim/index.xml" rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="RSS"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/grim/atom.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" title="Atom"/><updated>2021-04-19T02:41:01+00:00</updated><id>https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/grim/</id><entry><title type="html">Taken screenshots on SwayWM</title><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/taken-screenshots-on-swaywm/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id>https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/taken-screenshots-on-swaywm/</id><published>2021-03-22T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2021-03-22T00:00:00+00:00</updated><content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://swaywm.org/">SwayWM</a> uses can use a mixture of <a href="https://github.com/emersion/grim">grim</a> and <a href="https://github.com/emersion/slurp">slurp</a> to take screenshots of their desktop. Place the following key binding in your Sway config:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="c1"># take screenshot of currently focused screen</span>
bindsym <span class="nv">$mod</span>+Print <span class="nb">exec</span> /usr/bin/grim -o <span class="k">$(</span>swaymsg -t get_outputs <span class="p">|</span> jq -r <span class="s1">&#39;.[] | select(.focused) | .name&#39;</span><span class="k">)</span> <span class="k">$(</span>xdg-user-dir PICTURES<span class="k">)</span>/<span class="k">$(</span>date +<span class="s1">&#39;%Y-%m-%d-%H%M%S.png&#39;</span><span class="k">)</span>

<span class="c1"># take screenshot of selection</span>
bindsym <span class="nv">$mod</span>+Shift+p <span class="nb">exec</span> /usr/bin/grim -g <span class="s2">&#34;</span><span class="k">$(</span>/usr/bin/slurp<span class="k">)</span><span class="s2">&#34;</span> <span class="k">$(</span>xdg-user-dir PICTURES<span class="k">)</span>/<span class="k">$(</span>date +<span class="s1">&#39;%Y-%m-%d-%H%M%S.png&#39;</span><span class="k">)</span>
</code></pre></div>]]></content><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/categories/snippet" term="snippet" label="snippet"/><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/swaywm" term="swaywm" label="swaywm"/><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/screenshot" term="screenshot" label="screenshot"/><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/slurp" term="slurp" label="slurp"/><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/grim" term="grim" label="grim"/></entry></feed>